      <title>PG&E 因北加州野火风险而断电</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/pg-e-cuts-power-due-to-wildfire-risk-in-northern-california</link>
      <description><![CDATA[PG&amp;E 公司表示，已切断北加州数千名客户的电力，以防止其设备在阵风和干燥风中引发野火。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/pg-e-cuts-power-due-to-wildfire-risk-in-northern-california</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 18:56:50 GMT</pubDate>
