    <item>
      <title>港口工人罢工给拜登带来政治问题</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-30/port-worker-strike-poses-political-problems-for-biden-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[东部和墨西哥湾沿岸港口的码头工人罢工将给总统乔·拜登带来巨大的政治问题。截至目前，他说他不会介入。彭博社的丹尼·伯格在新泽西州纽瓦克-伊丽莎白港报道。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-30/port-worker-strike-poses-political-problems-for-biden-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 18:40:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>鲍威尔称美联储并不急于降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-30/powell-says-fed-doesn-t-feel-like-it-s-in-a-hurry-to-cut-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔表示，央行降息的速度取决于经济数据。他在纳什维尔举行的全国商业经济协会年会上发表讲话。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-30/powell-says-fed-doesn-t-feel-like-it-s-in-a-hurry-to-cut-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 18:37:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
