      <title>贸易商达成协议，向欧洲出口无森林砍伐咖啡</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/top-traders-start-selling-deforestation-free-coffee-to-europe</link>
      <description><![CDATA[全球最大的咖啡贸易商已开始承担额外的风险：在最终规则出台之前就向欧洲出售无森林砍伐的咖啡豆。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/top-traders-start-selling-deforestation-free-coffee-to-europe</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 17:55:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>高盛交易 10 亿英镑泰晤士水务公司债务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/goldman-trades-billions-in-thames-water-debt-as-hedge-funds-buy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[高盛集团 (Goldman Sachs Group Inc.) 9 月份执行了超过 10 亿英镑（13 亿美元）的泰晤士水务公司债券交易，为退出这家陷入困境的公用事业公司的原始投资者与以折扣价收购债务的投机者之间搭建了一个市场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/goldman-trades-billions-in-thames-water-debt-as-hedge-funds-buy</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 16:50:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>辉瑞将通过出售 Haleon 股份筹集 27 亿英镑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/pfizer-to-pare-back-haleon-stake-with-540-million-share-offering</link>
      <description><![CDATA[辉瑞公司准备通过出售 Haleon Plc 股份筹集约 27 亿英镑（36 亿美元），同时进一步减少其在英国消费健康巨头这家公司的股份。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/pfizer-to-pare-back-haleon-stake-with-540-million-share-offering</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 16:36:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
